 class=\"ffb-id-4s9a31pf fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Enjoy all things American this Independence Day with Caravelle Saigon&rsquo; best seafood buffet in town.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">You will be spoilt for choices with a wide selection of tempting appetizers and gourmet dishes from around the world, as well as unlimited premier meat cuts from barbecue and carving stations: turkey, honey ham, BBQ pork ribs... Don&rsquo;t forget to indulge in delicious dishes on offer include Nha Trang lobsters, blue crabs, bulots, selections of sushi &amp; sashimi and more&hellip;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Offer:<br \/>* U.S Celebration Buffet Dinner, only at VND 1,390,000++<br \/>* Soft drink, tea &amp; coffee included<br \/>* Offer applies only from July 3rd to July 5th 2022, from 17:45 to 22:00<\/p>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-5kmeiks0 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>More beverage selections:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* VND 299,000++ per person: House wines, cocktails of the day &amp; beers<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* Limited time offer on Champagne: 50% discount on any Champagne bottle<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Price is subject to 5% Service Charge &amp; 8% VAT<\/em><br \/><em>For more information, please call (84) 2838 234 999 or email: culinary@caravellehotel.com<\/em><\/p>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-4s9a31pg buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tablecheck.com\/en\/shops\/nineteen-buffet-restaurant\/reserve\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">BOOK YOUR TABLE<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section